The purpose: to develop a service stack for collecting, storing and exporting air pollution data to users.
1. The web scraping technology: packages-selenium and beautifulsoup, coding platform-jupyter lab/google colab
   Advantage: minimum reliance on computing environment setup and less hassle on instaling dependent libaries for coding test. Disadvantage: less secured for coding
2. backend: Geoserver, postGIS and postgresql.
   Advantage: open source with minumum maintenance; popular packages to gain technical community support; friendly with cloud environment. Disadvantage: maintenance requires expert skills.
3. frontend: QGIS/GRASS
   Advantage: open source package with minimum cost; active community support; user friendly compared to ArcGIS;intuitive to cope with python and R. Disadvantage: technical skills demanding.   
